  <brief_title>Impact of Symbiotic Administration on Intestinal Function of Head and Neck Patients Surgically Treated</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intestinal Function of Patients With Uper Air and Digestive Neoplasia Submitted to Surgical Treatment: Symbiotic Use Impact</official_title>
  <sponsors>
